"The copywriting is beautiful, and the art direction is wonderful."DDB Paris' whimsical "Emerging Species" entry for Hasbro's Play-Doh really caught the attention of Debbi Vandeven, Global CCO of VML and chair of the ADC Interactive jury. It's easy to see why. In the embedded video below she explains a bit more about why the work spoke to her.You can view this and other Art Directors’ Club and One Show entries by browsing this year’s entries and don’t miss the 97th Annual ADC Awards on 7 May 2018 and the One Show Creative Week Festival from 7 to 11 May 2018 in New York City – visit our One Show special section for all the latest updates.